    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;All Port Facility Security Officers (PFSOs) in the UK must attend an approved training course run by an accredited company. The companies in this document have thus far been accredited and received approval from the Department for Transport to conduct &lt;abbr title="Port Facility Security Officers"&gt;PFSO&lt;/abbr&gt; training courses on behalf of the industry. All courses may be subject to unannounced audits by the Department for Transport to ensure quality control. Additional training providers will be added to the list as they receive approval.&lt;/p&gt;

